  <Description>[H3]MC40A Light Cruiser[h3]
[P]The MC40a was a Mon Calamari capital ship commonly seen in the company of the much larger MC80a star cruiser. Considered by most commanders as a fleet support vessel, the MC40a was equipped with exceptionally powerful shields given its size. Each of these light cruisers is equipped with a squadron of starfighters to provide close support, along with several tractor beams and ion cannons for capturing enemy vessels.
[P][H4]&lt;fontsize=1&gt;Please see page 119 of the Strongholds of Resistance Sourcebook for details.[h4]</Description>
